snippet.title: Anomaly Agent: Action-Packed Indie Adventure Game - #devdiary
snippet.description:
Anomaly Agent is an action packed 2D Action & Adventure game. In our first "developer diary" video, we wanted to take a brief look at the story and action system of the game. 💣

🔗 Stay tuned for more and wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2378620/Anomaly_Agent/
